<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śuklasaṁvvatsara Āṣāḍa śuddha 10 guruvārāna pinakūnu <unclear>bā</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>cābattunki mollaguṁṭṭa kūniseṭṭi yiccina śāsanamuṁ
<lb n="3"/>kumārateluṁgurāyaniki 1200 veyinniyinū
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṟu ṭaṁkālaku ninnuṁ būṁṭaveṭṭi danamu veṭṭalēka sūra
<lb n="5" break="no"/>varapupekkaṁḍramuṁddaṟaṁ jēśina nirnayaṁ modalidha
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nānaku patramicci vaḍḍidhanāna<unclear>kai</unclear> nēṁ jēśina sugṛtālu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="7"/>Ākiripallini nē vēyiṁccina ceṟuvunnu Āceṟuvuvenaka
<lb n="8"/>tāḷunnu Āmāmiḷunnu Ā rāvulunnu yekkōṭigaṇā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lunnu brāhmalakuṁ jēyiṁcina vaḍugulu peṇṇiṁḍlu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nnu A<unclear>ti</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">dhi</supplied>Abhyāgatikiṁ beṭṭina sugrutālunnu yiṁttava
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṭu nīku yistini <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yiṁduku sākṣi Aṣṭulōkadharma
<lb n="12" break="no"/>pālasākṣi śrīśrīśrīśrīśrī
</p>

